<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 14:07:18 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>内塔尼亚胡尽管呼吁在战争中避免政治，但仍在与利库德集团的亲信进行会谈</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-engages-in-political-consultations-despite-own-calls-to-avoid-it-amid-war/0000018c-62c1-d6f9-afbc-7fcb16f50000</link><description>最近与总理关系密切的立法者和顾问举行了磋商，讨论了内塔尼亚胡有关《奥斯陆协议》的信息以及确保本尼·甘茨所在政党的吉迪恩·萨尔部长继续担任内阁成员的方法</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 13:27:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-engages-in-political-consultations-despite-own-calls-to-avoid-it-amid-war/0000018c-62c1-d6f9-afbc-7fcb16f50000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日的大屠杀让这位伊拉克犹太作家回想起可怕的回忆</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/books/2023-12-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-october-7-massacre-brings-back-horrific-memories-for-this-iraqi-jewish-author/0000018c-62c5-dbd5-a39c-fff7971b0000</link><description>1969 年 1 月，九名犹太人因间谍罪被判在巴格达被绞死。几分钟路程外，15 岁的莫娜·叶海亚 (Mona Yahia) 因为害怕人群而躲在家里。这些景象仍然新鲜，并在她的新半自传小说中被精美地捕捉到</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 12:29:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/books/2023-12-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-october-7-massacre-brings-back-horrific-memories-for-this-iraqi-jewish-author/0000018c-62c5-dbd5-a39c-fff7971b0000</guid></item><item><title>在罕见批评后，拜登派遣高级顾问前往以色列就加沙战争时间表进行会谈</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/.premium/after-rare-critique-of-israel-biden-dispatches-top-adviser-for-talks-on-gaza-timetable/0000018c-628f-d6f9-afbc-7fcf2a910000</link><description>以色列官员担心，美国国家安全顾问抵达以色列后，美国将在几周内结束加沙战争的最后期限。其他来访的美国高级官员也有这样的印象：内塔尼亚胡寻求在加沙“后天”与拜登公开对抗</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 11:03:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/.premium/after-rare-critique-of-israel-biden-dispatches-top-adviser-for-talks-on-gaza-timetable/0000018c-628f-d6f9-afbc-7fcf2a910000</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，尽管初步就条款进行了谈判，但以色列与哈马斯续签人质协议仍遥遥无期</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/.premium/renewed-israeli-hamas-hostage-deal-distant-despite-initial-talks-for-terms-sources-say/0000018c-6253-dbd5-a39c-ff73a5360000</link><description>一名以色列官员估计，哈马斯可能会试图推动一项新的协议，以进一步缓解以色列国防军战斗中的挫折。虽然哈马斯的目标是推进一项“所有人为所有人”的协议，但据报道，以色列更愿意寻求一项植根于人道主义原则的协议</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 09:40:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/.premium/renewed-israeli-hamas-hostage-deal-distant-despite-initial-talks-for-terms-sources-say/0000018c-6253-dbd5-a39c-ff73a5360000</guid></item><item><title>加沙地带北部9名以色列士兵丧生的战斗背后</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/eight-israeli-soldiers-including-idf-brigade-commander-killed-in-gaza-fighting/0000018c-617b-d798-adac-e5ff9ac80000</link><description>在舒贾耶耶被杀的士兵是恐怖武装分子向在该地区活动的以色列国防军开火时发起的协同伏击的受害者。一旦担心他们可能被绑架到附近的隧道，另一支部队赶来解救士兵，却遭遇了类似的伏击</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 07:12:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/eight-israeli-soldiers-including-idf-brigade-commander-killed-in-gaza-fighting/0000018c-617b-d798-adac-e5ff9ac80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对哈马斯的军事优势在加沙北部拥挤的城市地区被削弱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/.premium/israels-military-edge-over-hamas-is-blunted-in-crowded-areas-of-northern-gaza/0000018c-5fe4-dbd5-a39c-fff7003f0000</link><description>以色列国防军仍未控制 Shujaiyeh，但在 Jabalya 难民营遇到的阻力有所减少 ■ 尽管人质处境悲惨，但以色列政府似乎并不急于达成另一项协议 ■ 没有迹象表明哈马斯认为其谈判地位已经恶化</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 04:00:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/.premium/israels-military-edge-over-hamas-is-blunted-in-crowded-areas-of-northern-gaza/0000018c-5fe4-dbd5-a39c-fff7003f0000</guid></item><item><title>十名以色列国防军士兵在加沙战斗中丧生；以色列外长：无论有没有国际支持，战争都会继续</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article-live/report-israel-flooding-hamas-tunnels-idf-retrieves-bodies-of-two-hostages-from-gaza/0000018c-6126-d798-adac-e5af76d80000</link><description>周二，九名以色列国防军士兵在加沙地带北部的舒贾耶地区遭到伏击身亡，其中一人在附近的另一起事件中丧生 ■ 据《华尔街日报》报道，以色列开始向哈马斯隧道注入海水 ■ 从加沙遣返的两名以色列人质的尸体 ■拜登：内塔尼亚胡“必须改变他的政府”，以色列因加沙狂轰滥炸而失去支持 ■ 以色列国防军更新战争中受伤士兵人数至 1,645 名 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列至少有 1,200 名平民和士兵丧生；超过 138 名人质仍被扣押在加沙 ■ 哈马斯卫生部声称 18,608 人死亡，50,594 人受伤</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 03:19:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article-live/report-israel-flooding-hamas-tunnels-idf-retrieves-bodies-of-two-hostages-from-gaza/0000018c-6126-d798-adac-e5af76d80000</guid></item><item><title>罗格斯大学加入了越来越多打压亲巴勒斯坦学生团体的大学行列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/.premium/rutgers-joins-growing-list-of-universities-clamping-down-on-pro-palestinian-student-group/0000018c-6031-dbd5-a39c-ff7371350000</link><description>巴勒斯坦正义学生会周一接到通知，其罗格斯-新不伦瑞克分会已被暂停，因为收到多起投诉，称其扰乱了课堂、项目、膳食和学生学习</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 02:17:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/.premium/rutgers-joins-growing-list-of-universities-clamping-down-on-pro-palestinian-student-group/0000018c-6031-dbd5-a39c-ff7371350000</guid></item><item><title>加沙的发病率危及哈马斯扣押的人质，很快甚至会危及以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/.premium/morbidity-in-gaza-endangers-the-hostages-and-possibly-israel/0000018c-5fe1-d6f9-afbc-5febf3e60000</link><description>加沙人面临着多种疾病的风险，这些疾病不能仅限于政治边界。 “我估计几周之内我们就会开始在以色列感受到这一点。本古里安大学公共卫生学院的一位高级健康学者说：“最初，它将在南部地区传播，然后由士兵传播。”</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 01:01:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/.premium/morbidity-in-gaza-endangers-the-hostages-and-possibly-israel/0000018c-5fe1-d6f9-afbc-5febf3e60000</guid></item><item><title>专家警告以色列政府法案提议总理允许辛贝特秘密搜查手机和电脑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/.premium/experts-amendment-to-surveillance-law-would-give-israeli-pm-great-power-without-oversight/0000018c-5fc7-de43-affd-ffc7136f0000</link><description>专家：监视法修正案将赋予以色列总理不受监督的巨大权力。以色列政府希望让 Shin Bet 使用间谍软件秘密搜索手机和计算机，并访问包含其“完成工作所需”信息的数据库</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 00:30:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/.premium/experts-amendment-to-surveillance-law-would-give-israeli-pm-great-power-without-oversight/0000018c-5fc7-de43-affd-ffc7136f0000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔呼吁未经认证的女兵处理枪支许可证的发放</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-calls-on-uncertified-national-service-women-to-handle-gun-permits-issuing/0000018c-5ed1-dbd5-a39c-fff38cb00000</link><description>本-格维尔在获得法律批准之前就批准了该职位的广告，消息人士称，这位极右翼部长这样做是为了获得政治分数。执照办事员应该仔细审查申请人，确保他们符合拥有枪支的心理和身体健康要求</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 21:05:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-calls-on-uncertified-national-service-women-to-handle-gun-permits-issuing/0000018c-5ed1-dbd5-a39c-fff38cb00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警察局长任命本-格维尔高级职员加入西岸警察</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/.premium/israels-police-chief-appoints-a-senior-member-of-ben-gvirs-office-to-west-bank-police/0000018c-5da3-d6f9-afbc-5deb5d810000</link><description>消息人士称，更适合该职位的候选人被拒绝，其中一位消息人士称，本-格维尔“想指派一名自己的人”到以色列最敏感的警察区之一</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 20:09:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/.premium/israels-police-chief-appoints-a-senior-member-of-ben-gvirs-office-to-west-bank-police/0000018c-5da3-d6f9-afbc-5deb5d810000</guid></item><item><title>以色列正处于战争状态，内塔尼亚胡刚刚发起连任竞选</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-is-at-war-and-netanyahu-just-launched-his-re-election-campaign/0000018c-5f3f-de43-affd-ff3ff7c60000</link><description>本杰明·内塔尼亚胡在民意调查中严重落后，并且正处于加沙与哈马斯的血腥冲突之中，他希望将以色列人在 10 月 7 日之后的创伤和愤怒转化为自己的选举需求</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 19:43:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-is-at-war-and-netanyahu-just-launched-his-re-election-campaign/0000018c-5f3f-de43-affd-ff3ff7c60000</guid></item><item><title>拜登称以色列因加沙爆炸事件失去国际支持，内塔尼亚胡必须“改变”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/biden-says-israel-losing-support-over-gaza-bombings-netanyahu-must-change-his-government/0000018c-5f60-d798-adac-ffef14800000</link><description>美国总统表示，以色列不能对巴勒斯坦国说不，这进一步表明美国对以色列轰炸加沙的行为日益担忧。周二早些时候，内塔尼亚胡表示，以色列和美国在“哈马斯之后的第二天”计划存在分歧</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 19:36:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/biden-says-israel-losing-support-over-gaza-bombings-netanyahu-must-change-his-government/0000018c-5f60-d798-adac-ffef14800000</guid></item><item><title>忘记美国大学校长吧，我们应该担心他们的犹太学生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-12-12/ty-article/.highlight/forget-u-s-college-heads-we-should-worry-about-their-jewish-students/0000018c-5f6a-de43-affd-ff6ac27a0000</link><description>当暴力呼吁变成“行为”时，就为时已晚了。美国的犹太学生怎么能像这样生活，时刻关心自己的福祉呢？他们怎么能时刻保持警惕呢？</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 19:18:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-12-12/ty-article/.highlight/forget-u-s-college-heads-we-should-worry-about-their-jewish-students/0000018c-5f6a-de43-affd-ff6ac27a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方称13名在加沙被杀的士兵被误认为是哈马斯成员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-says-13-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-were-mistakenly-identified-as-hamas-members/0000018c-5e46-dbd5-a39c-ff770e560000</link><description>以色列军队补充说，另有七名士兵在战争期间的其他行动事故中丧生。自地面行动开始以来，迄今已有105名士兵在加沙丧生</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 16:07:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-says-13-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-were-mistakenly-identified-as-hamas-members/0000018c-5e46-dbd5-a39c-ff770e560000</guid></item><item><title>考古学家对将圣经中的耶路撒冷一分为二的巨大护城河感到困惑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-12-12/ty-article/archaeologists-bewildered-by-monumental-moat-that-split-biblical-jerusalem-in-two/0000018c-5eac-d6f9-afbc-5feeab320000</link><description>以色列考古学家发现了一条刻在岩石上的巨大沟渠，这条沟渠可能在 3000 年前将古耶路撒冷一分为二，精英分子在一边，其余的人在另一边。为什么是另一个问题</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 15:52:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-12-12/ty-article/archaeologists-bewildered-by-monumental-moat-that-split-biblical-jerusalem-in-two/0000018c-5eac-d6f9-afbc-5feeab320000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡办公室获得数百万美元资助以色列最新预算中的信息宣传活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-office-gets-millions-to-fund-info-campaigns-in-israels-updated-budget/0000018c-5e9b-dbd5-a39c-fffb6fcd0000</link><description>部分资金将流向一个拥有自己的广播团队的内部电视工作室，批评者称这将是国家控制的媒体，公共外交部已被解散</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 15:48:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-office-gets-millions-to-fund-info-campaigns-in-israels-updated-budget/0000018c-5e9b-dbd5-a39c-fffb6fcd0000</guid></item><item><title>犹太人和巴勒斯坦人都是西方种族主义的受害者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article-opinion/.premium/jews-and-palestinians-are-both-victims-of-western-racism/0000018c-5e28-d6f9-afbc-5f6a74e10000</link><description>与背景无关的震惊和悲伤加上对冲突各个方面的法律解释是不够的。必须研究的是一般的历史叙述。在那之前，以色列与哈马斯战争的唯一赢家将是战争本身</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 15:04:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article-opinion/.premium/jews-and-palestinians-are-both-victims-of-western-racism/0000018c-5e28-d6f9-afbc-5f6a74e10000</guid></item><item><title>“即使是所有以色列人质回家的照片也不会是胜利的形象”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/even-a-picture-of-all-the-hostages-returning-home-wouldnt-be-an-image-of-victory/0000018c-5d91-de43-affd-fd93d60e0000</link><description>当前的战争相当于 1967 年以色列伞兵在西墙充满敬畏的标志性照片吗？专家解释了为什么即使是哈马斯领导人叶海亚辛瓦尔尸体的照片也无法消除10月7日的恐怖画面所带来的失落感</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 14:58:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/even-a-picture-of-all-the-hostages-returning-home-wouldnt-be-an-image-of-victory/0000018c-5d91-de43-affd-fd93d60e0000</guid></item></channel></rss>